# Title: Control Panel Items
# Author: Kyaw Min Thein, Furkan Caliskan (@caliskanfurkan_)
# Date: 2020-06-22
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the malicious use of a control panel item
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.execution, attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1218.002, attack.persistence, attack.t1546

(CommandLine="*add*" CommandLine="*CurrentVersion\\Control Panel\\CPLs*" Image="*\\reg.exe" OR OriginalFileName="reg.exe") OR (CommandLine="*.cpl" NOT ((CommandLine="*regsvr32 *" CommandLine="* /s *" CommandLine="*igfxCPL.cpl*") OR CommandLine IN ("*\\System32\\*", "*%System%*", "*|C:\\Windows\\system32|*")))